long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A personalize and beautiful, customize home portal website tab page for Chrome, Firefox, Edge and all chromium based browser.

No subscription needed. No ads. Absolutely Free.

Personalized experience on new tabs for better productivity

Szwsaoyika.io New Tab is an extension for improving your browsing experience. Each new tab will be filled with a random image to remind you of to the beautiful places in the world. All images are subtitled by the photographer's name and whenever possible, the location where the photo was taken. New tabs will also contain the current time as well as a nice greeting. In addtion, new tabs are enriched by a motivational quote which will be updated each day!

All images displayed are served by unsplash.com from a collection.
All photos published on Unsplash can be used for free. 
You can use them for commercial and noncommercial purposes. 
You do not need to ask permission from or provide credit to the photographer or Unsplash, although it is appreciated when possible.
